OL,3,C'Reckless and selfish driver' killed
OL,4,Cinnocent man as he cycled to work
OL,6,FA motorist who crashed into a cyclist
OL,7,Fin St Helens and left him to die has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for more than six years.
OL,10,FAnya Foster, 32, of Gloucester Street
OL,11,Fthe town, was driving a Skoda Fabia on
OL,12,FFriday 1 December 2023, when she hit
OL,13,F59-year-old David Burrows who was
OL,14,Friding his bike to work.
OL,16,FDavid was taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment but sadly died of his
OL,18,Finjuries shortly afterwards.
