OL,3,C'Reckless and selfish driver' killed
OL,4,Cinnocent man as he cycled to work
OL,6,FInstead of staying at the scene to
OL,7,Fhelp, Foster drove off. She was
OL,8,Farrested later that same day after
OL,9,Fdriving home.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Simon Duffy from
OL,12,Fthe Matrix Serious Collision
OL,13,FInvestigation Unit said: "Foster's
OL,14,Freckless and selfish driving resulted
OL,15,Fin the death of an innocent man whilst
OL,16,Fhe was riding to work, completely
OL,17,Fdevastating his family.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU
