OL,3,C'Reckless and selfish driver' killed
OL,4,Cinnocent man as he cycled to work
OL,6,F"Not only did she cause the crash, but
OL,7,Frather than stop at the scene to help
OL,8,FDavid and face the consequences of her
OL,9,Factions, she chose to flee and began
OL,10,Fto weave a web of lies.
OL,12,F"Our investigation proved that Foster
OL,13,Fattempted to mislead officers at
OL,14,Fmultiple stages. We have worked
OL,15,Ftirelessly to establish the full facts
OL,16,Fand Foster has now been held
OL,17,Faccountable for her actions.
