OL,3,C'Reckless and selfish driver' killed
OL,4,Cinnocent man as he cycled to work
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain firmly with
OL,7,FDavid's family and friends as they
OL,8,Fcontinue to deal with the devastating
OL,9,Foutcome of this heartbreaking incident
OL,10,Fevery day."
OL,12,FFoster pleaded guilty to causing death
OL,13,Fby careless driving while over the
OL,14,Flimit for two separate controlled
OL,15,Fsubstances, driving whilst unfit
OL,16,Fthrough drugs, failing to stop after a
OL,17,Fcollision and failing to report a
OL,18,Fcollision.
OL,20,FShe was sentenced to six years and
OL,21,Feight months at Liverpool Crown Court.
